			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				*and nods almost seemingly caring to the knight* <br>  <br> Dear knight do tell me true, you made comment to a &quot;she's not here&quot; earlier.  Who is this &quot;she&quot;? <br>  <br> Who is it that you obviously pine so for?  Is this &quot;she&quot; your wife or is this &quot;she&quot; your lover? <br>  <br> Not that I would understand such a concept of love of course, but I do understand having a warm heart on rare occassion. <br>  <br> *wraps her red ringleted polar cloak around her and absorbs the heat of the hearth*		

