				*...cocks her head, and smiles at the gentleman and dark elf* <br>  <br> Aye, true, but isn't Tunare a mother figure? So there is such a love in her.  <br>  <br> *She narrows her eyes playfully, wrinkling her nose* <br>  <br> So perhaps you aren't that far off... <br>  <br> *Mailea stabnds abruptly, brushing her hands off on her greaves and extends them* <br>  <br> I am Mailea Charmheart, dashing wood elf bardess... would you mind making my aqquaintance? <br>  <br> *Her eyes twinkle merrily, glowing off the firelight*		

