			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				Indeed Lady, love appears to be a poison deadlier by far then even thy most noxious brew. <br>  <br> I fear you have misunderstood my words.  I serve Tunare and as such my comment was intended to imply that I ought to be happy to accept Her will in this.  Well happy I am not but as She wills it... <br>  <br> *Lothannon pauses for a moment, choosing his words with care* <br>  <br> As for Erolisi, I have little time for Her.  It is my humble opinion that she is merely the reflection of a facet of Tunare in any case.  After all a Mother is surely the ultimate source of all love. <br>  <br> Ah and my sincere thanks for thy offer lady...*Lothannon's eyes sparkle briefly*...but I believe I am past the self destructive phase now.		

