				The shaman's homely face splits into a wide grin as Gutrot goes about his antics.  &quot;Is gud to see anudda brudda outside da swamp,&quot; he rumbles, his voice soft as stones rolling down a hill in contrast to Gutrot's avalanche.  &quot;You been down dere lately?  Any rumor goin' round bout Kaglari's brood?  Been a long time since dis troll wuz sloggin' t'rough da Innnothule, an I do no hear tings about my brudda shaman dis far nort'.&quot;  After a pause and an angry glance at the thin air to his left, he murmurs almost inaudibly, &quot;Not frum peoples, anyway.&quot; <br>  <br> His attention is drawn away momentarily from his boisterous brother troll to the other fresh face in the room.  His grin decreasing to a gentler smile, he nods his head respectfully in the direction of Mailea.  &quot;Hallo, elfie ladee, an' welcome.  I is Cyst Spiritseeker, a mojo troll of da Tribunal. Is gud to meet you.&quot;
